precis:
Acceptance of an Instrument wherein the OSOYOOS INDIAN BAND amends the
Designation (for leasing purposes) it made on December 7, 1979, by
designating two additional lots for leasing, extending the term of the
surrender and restricting the purposes for which the lands can be leased.
